<a class="title" href="/nodes/97054/comments/1423851">Re: Une vraie question</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/coin--2" rel="author">coïn</a> <time class="updated" datetime="2013-01-15T15:05:33+01:00"><span class="date">le 15/01/13</span> <span class="time">à 15:05</span></time>.
