<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/flagos" rel="author">flagos</a> (<a href="http://blog.lilibio.com/">page perso</a>) <time class="updated" datetime="2013-01-16T11:01:56+01:00"><span class="date">le 16/01/13</span> <span class="time">à 11:01</span></time>.
