<figure class="image"><img alt="" class="avatar" height="64" src="//img.linuxfr.org/avatars/687474703a2f2f7777772e67726176617461722e636f6d2f6176617461722f36346562303566653730623866333737363732346263323364373661383938362e706e67/64eb05fe70b8f3776724bc23d76a8986.png" width="64" /></figure>
